# Solving military alignment

There are two cases that the AI must solve before you can trust it with military alignment

## 4d Chess

You must solve 4D chess with Multiverse time travel for the two player case.

## MTG Commander
Then you must solve a four player/N player magic the gathering Commander game.

You must attempt to solve with known and unknown decks. Known decks are easy using Facebook Meta research Rebel poker AI . Then you must accelerate the path splitting for every magic gathering case on the GPU . This lets you easily solve for the known case . After you solve for the known case, you can attempt the unknown case.

The four player dialogue dynamic is crucial. Establishing trust, game theory.


